VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT implementation\s+['"][\w\.-]+:\w+:\d+\.\d+\.\d+['"]
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:com\.android\.tools|androidx|google|okhttp|retrofit|firebase
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects dependency declarations with version numbers in the Gradle file.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Outdated Dependencies.
